Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.65,0:05:46.41,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}向前划行  向前划行
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.41,0:05:48.75,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}要去哪里呢
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.75,0:05:50.96,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}无论去哪里
